<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Overview</strong></span>
</p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Coach and player registration is required</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">March 16&nbsp;- May 22, 2026</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Ages 4 - 12&nbsp;years old (Based on age as of April 1, 2026)</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">All leagues are coed</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Registration fee is $157 for all participants</span><ul>
		<li><span style="font-size:16px;">All payments should be made by credit card at the time of registration</span><span style="font-size:16px;"></span><span style="font-size:16px;"></span></li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our pre-game devotions and prayers for each sport.</span></li>
</ul>

<p>
