</p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Practices will start on March 16,&nbsp;2026&nbsp;(scheduled on weekdays based on coach availability)</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Games will start the week of April 6, 2026 (scheduled on weekdays based on coach availability)</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">If there aren't enough 4-year-olds for their own league they will play with the 5-6 year-olds.</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">All players will bat from a tee</span></li>
