<div style="background-color:#2A313F;color:#FFFFFF;padding:40px;" data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:40:4"><h2>Flag Football</h2>

<p>
	<span style="font-size:16px;"><strong>Overview</strong></span>
</p>

<ul>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Registration is required for all coaches, assistants,&nbsp;and players</span></li>
	<li>Player registration fee&nbsp;is&nbsp;$157</li>
	<li><span style="font-size: 16px;">This is a seven-week&nbsp;program that runs from October 13&nbsp;through December 5, 2025</span></li>
	<li>Coach registration is now open</li>
	<li>Player registration is now open</li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">Ages: 7-12 (based on child’s age as of October 1, 2025)</span></span><ul>
		<li>7-8-year-old league</li>
		<li>9–10-year-old league</li>
		<li>11–12-year-old league</li>
		<li>If we do not have enough participants in each league, we will combine the 7–9-year-olds and 10-12 year-olds</li>
	</ul>
	</li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Practice dates are from October 13&nbsp;through October 31, 2025</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Game&nbsp;dates are from November 3&nbsp;through December 5, 2025</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">Mouthpiece is required</span></li>
	<li><span style="font-size:16px;">A Christ-centered atmosphere is maintained in our pre-game devotions and prayers for each sport.</span><span style="font-size:16px;"></span></li>
</ul>

