<h5 data-zesty-id="content:text:54:99">Open Gym</h5>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:55:43">
	Our Open Gym membership gives you unlimited access to pickup basketball and pickleball for the entire month. With your membership, checking in is simple and hassle-free.
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:56:26">
	Please note:
</p>
<ul data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:57:80">
	<li><span style="tab-stops:list .5in;">Memberships are valid only for the month in which they are purchased. ($5 per day for non-members)</span></li>
	<li><span style="tab-stops:list .5in;">Renewals are required monthly to continue participation</span></li>
	<li><span style="tab-stops:list .5in;">Cost is $38 ($35 Flat rate + $3 PayPal surcharge)</span></li>
</ul>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:58:72"></div>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:59:46">
	We’re excited to have you join us and hope you enjoy everything our Open Gym program has to offer!
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:60:47">
	Pickleball: Thursdays 3-6 p.m.&nbsp;(Will add days as participation grows)
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:textarea:61:25">
	Basketball: Monday, Wednesday, Friday 11:30 a.m. - 1:30 p.m.
</p>
